# Firmware Private Libraries

No project-private PlatformIO libraries are currently kept in this folder.

The firmware currently uses PlatformIO `lib_deps` from `platformio.ini`:

- `nrf24/RF24`
- `bblanchon/ArduinoJson`
- `links2004/WebSockets`

Add a subdirectory here only when code is truly shared across firmware modules
and does not belong in `src`/`include`.
